        "action": "Make taxation a compulsory part of the National Curriculum",
        "additional_details": "People do not understand what they need to do and I feel if they got taught this basic knowledge then less people would get in trouble with the law. The website could be confusing for some and as some students will be entering the world of work, I feel like this lesson would benefit them.",
